2 tablespoons fresh lime salt to taste 
¼ cup chopped fresh cilantro

Rustic Fish Recipe! This recipe is absolutely delicious. It’s so easy and I can’t wait for you to try! 

Ingredients- 
Yellow Gold fresh tomatoes (This is Key)
Garlic 
Fresh Oregano 
Salt and Pepper 
Olive oil 
Juice of one lemon
Red and white Baby Potatoes 
Rosemary 
Fresh Flounder or any white fish 

Bake Tomatoes and Potatoes at 415 degrees for 20mins or until potatoes are a little brown. Then place fish on top and bake again for 15mins. Let cool and it’s ready to serve.
